---
import Introduction from "../components/Introduction.astro";
import Projects from "../components/Projects.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="\Logo.png" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>portfolio</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-zinc-950 text-white font-sans flex flex-col">
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <header
      class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto"
    >
      <nav>
        <ul class="flex space-x-6">
          <li>
            <button
              class="text-sm font-medium text-white bg-transparent hover:bg-gray-700 px-3 py-2 rounded"
            >
              Projects
            </button>
          </li>
          <li>
            <button
              class="text-sm font-medium text-white bg-transparent hover:bg-gray-700 px-3 py-2 rounded"
            >
              About
            </button>
          </li>
          <li>
            <button
              class="text-sm font-medium text-white bg-transparent hover:bg-gray-700 px-3 py-2 rounded"
            >
              Contact
            </button>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <button
        class="text-sm font-medium text-white border border-white px-3 py-2 rounded"
      >
        ENG ▼
      </button>
    </header>
    <!-- Content -->
    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <Introduction />
      <Projects />
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-5 grid-rows-[repeat(12,minmax(0,1fr))] gap-6 max-w-6xl w-full m-32"
      >
        <!-- At Work Section -->
        <section
          class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 col-span-3 row-span-6"
          aria-labelledby="work-heading"
        >
          <h2
            id="work-heading"
            class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center"
          >
            <span class="mr-2 text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">□</span> At Work
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Although I’m seeking my <strong>first professional opportunity</strong>, I bring a strong <strong>eagerness to learn</strong> and <strong>adapt</strong>. I value a <strong>collaborative and supportive team environment</strong> where <strong>skills are recognized</strong> and a <strong>positive culture</strong> is fostered.
          </p>
          <p>
            Above all, I believe that being a <strong>good person</strong> comes before being a good <strong>developer</strong>. While I’m dedicated to <strong>growing as a professional</strong> and striving to excel, I prioritize <strong>supporting and respecting others</strong>, ensuring a <strong>harmonious and empathetic workplace</strong>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- My personal side Section -->
        <section
          class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 col-span-2 row-span-8 col-start-4 row-start-1"
          aria-labelledby="personal-heading"
        >
          <h2
            id="personal-heading"
            class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center"
          >
            <span class="mr-2 text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">□</span> My personal side
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            <strong>Resilient</strong>, <strong>curious</strong>, and <strong>benevolent</strong>—these three words best define me. I wasn't always naturally skilled at connecting with people, so I took the initiative to learn through <strong>psychology content</strong>, which taught me to be <strong>trustworthy</strong>, <strong>listen actively</strong>, and <strong>collaborate effectively</strong>.
          </p>
          <p>
            I've always been naturally <strong>curious</strong>, not only looking to learn new things but also to <strong>understand</strong> them. <strong>Asking questions</strong> and <strong>figuring out how things work</strong> is my passion. Whether <strong>coding</strong> or <strong>learning new skills</strong>, I approach everything with <strong>resilience</strong> and a <strong>benevolent mindset</strong>, staying <strong>focused</strong> and <strong>positive</strong> even in the face of obstacles.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Languages Section -->
        <section
          class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 col-span-3 row-span-2 col-start-1 row-start-7"
          aria-labelledby="languages-heading"
        >
          <h2
            id="languages-heading"
            class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center"
          >
            <span class="mr-2 text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">□</span> Languages
          </h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li>English B2 - Certification</li>
            <li>Japanese N6</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Location Section -->
        <section
          class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 col-span-2 row-span-5 col-start-1 row-start-9 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center"
          aria-labelledby="location-heading"
        >
          <h2
            id="location-heading"
            class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center self-start w-full"
          >
            <span class="mr-2 text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">□</span> Location
          </h2>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Based in Argentina</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-6">5h ahead of you</p>
          <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-700 mb-6"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mr-2"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline
                points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg
            >
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold">2:56 PM</span>
            <span class="ml-2 text-lg">GMT-3</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg">Sunday, August 25</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Technologies Section -->
        <section
          class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 col-span-3 row-span-5 col-start-3 row-start-9"
          aria-labelledby="technologies-heading"
        >
          <h2
            id="technologies-heading"
            class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center"
          >
            <span class="mr-2 text-3xl" aria-hidden="true">□</span> Technologies
          </h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <!-- Repeat this div 12 times for the technology icons -->
            <div
              class="bg-gray-700 p-4 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <img
                src="/placeholder.svg"
                alt="Technology icon 1"
                class="w-12 h-12"
              />
            </div>
            
            <!-- ... Repeat 11 more times ... -->
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
        <div class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Contact me</h2>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Get in touch</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
                Feel free to reach out through any of these platforms:
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="flex items-center text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors"
                >
                  <i class="far fa-envelope mr-2"></i>
                  your.email@example.com
                </a>
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="flex items-center text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors"
                >
                  <i class="fab fa-github mr-2"></i>
                  GitHub
                </a>
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="flex items-center text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors"
                >
                  <i class="fab fa-linkedin mr-2"></i>
                  LinkedIn
                </a>
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="flex items-center text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors"
                >
                  <i class="fab fa-twitter mr-2"></i>
                  Twitter
                </a>
                <a
                  href="#"
                  class="flex items-center text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors"
                >
                  <i class="fab fa-instagram mr-2"></i>
                  Instagram
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
              <form class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <label
                    for="name"
                    class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mb-1"
                    >Name</label
                  >
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    id="name"
                    name="name"
                    placeholder="Your name"
                    class="w-full px-3 py-2 bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-md text-white"
                  />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label
                    for="email"
                    class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mb-1"
                    >Email</label
                  >
                  <input
                    type="email"
                    id="email"
                    name="email"
                    placeholder="Your email"
                    class="w-full px-3 py-2 bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-md text-white"
                  />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label
                    for="message"
                    class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mb-1"
                    >Message</label
                  >
                  <textarea
                    id="message"
                    name="message"
                    rows="4"
                    placeholder="Your message"
                    class="w-full px-3 py-2 bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-md text-white"
                  ></textarea>
                </div>
                <button
                  type="submit"
                  class="w-full bg-white text-black font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded"
                >
                  Send Message
                </button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Footer + Copyright -->
      <footer class="text-center py-6 text-gray-400 border-t border-gray-800">
        <p>
          © <span id="current-year"></span> YOUR NAME. All rights reserved. Built
          with HTML, Tailwind CSS, and Font Awesome. Deployed on [Your Hosting Platform].
        </p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
